{"type":"message","id":"472045fa","parentId":"63e2433f","timestamp":"2026-03-02T12:45:04.556Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm unable to directly install the skill for you in this environment, but here's how you can set it up manually to ensure the Nashville brief runs:\n\n1. **Create a standalone script** for the Nashville brief:\n```bash\necho '#!/bin/bash\n# Nashville Brief Script - 6:30am & 4:00pm\n\n# Get car status\ncar_status=$(tessie parse car status)\n\n# Get local news (Nashville focus)\nnews=$(curl -s \"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=Nashville technology business cryptocurrency\")\n\n# Get traffic info\ntraffic=$(curl -s \"https://api.tomtom.com/routing/1/calculateCarRoutes/2.0/\\{jsonp:\\&point=36.1657%2C-86.7777\\&point=36.1455%2C-86.7878\\}/response.json\")\n\n# Format output\necho \"=== 6:30 AM Nashville Brief ===\"\necho \"🚗 Car Status: $car_status\"\necho \"🗞️ Local News Highlights:\"\necho \"$news\" | head -n 10 | tail -n 2\necho \"🚦 Traffic Conditions:\"\necho \"$traffic\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 4:00 PM Nashville Brief ===\"\necho \"🚗 Car Status: $car_status\"\necho \"🗞️ Local News Highlights:\"\necho \"$news\" | tail -n 1\necho \"🚦 Traffic Conditions:\"\necho \"$traffic\"' > /home/ec2-user/.openclaw/workspace/tools/nashville_brief.sh\n\n# Make it executable\nchmod +x /home/ec2-user/.openclaw/workspace/tools/nashville_brief.sh\n```\n\n2. **Update your crontab** with these new jobs:\n```bash\n# Run at 6:30 AM and 4:00 PM daily\n30 6 * * * /home/ec2-user/.openclaw/workspace/tools/nashville_brief.sh\n0 16 * * * /home/ec2-user/.openclaw/workspace/tools/nashville_brief.sh\n```\n\n3. **Verify cron jobs** were added successfully:\n```bash\ncrontab -l\n```\n\nThis setup should:\n- Run at both required times\n- Include car status, 2 news lines, and traffic info\n- Use system tools you already have (curl for web data)\n- Create a standalone script for easy testing\n\nWould you like me to:\n1. Test the script now for sample output?\n2. Adjust any part of the content or format?\n3. Help you verify the cron jobs are active?\n\n>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/free","usage":{"input":42772,"output":567,"cacheRead":1104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44443,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772455486724}}
