{"type":"message","id":"643de0a1","parentId":"7cb993c2","timestamp":"2026-03-02T15:34:38.509Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The system doesn't see `tessie` in the PATH. This could be due to:\n- Global install instead of workspace install\n- Path issues in OpenClaw's tool configuration\n- Environment variables not loading correctly\n\nLet's verify and fix:\n\n1. **Check for workspace-specific path**  \n```bash\nopenclaw skills list | grep tessie\n```\n\n2. **If tessie isn't in PATH**  \nWe'll need to either:\n- Install it directly to `/usr/bin`\n- Add workspace bin to PATH via `openclaw` config\n- Use `npx` to execute it locally\n\nWhich approach would you prefer? I can help fix this quickly."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/free","usage":{"input":65082,"output":141,"cacheRead":208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65431,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772465658611}}
